title: Haloumi & Creamy Pesto Roast Veggie Salad with Roasted Almonds & Herbs
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that makes you feel whole, happy and healthy all at once. Flavourful haloumi meets roasted
vegetables tossed with golden spices, and there’s a garlicky yoghurt drizzle and toasted almonds to finish it off.

